OL,3,CThree men who carried out 'frenzied'
OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FThree burglars have been jailed for
OL,7,Fmore than 43 years after a "frenzied"
OL,8,Fattack in Redruth, which left one
OL,9,Fvictim lucky to be alive.
OL,11,FPaul Amoah, Lee Mitchell and Gavin
OL,12,FSmale were all sentenced after they
OL,13,Fbroke into a property in the town
OL,14,Farmed with a gun and hammer, seriously
OL,15,Finjuring two people.
OL,17,FOne victim was shot during the break-
OL,18,Fin and the bullet, which is still
OL,19,Flodged in his chest, missed his heart
OL,20,Fby just two milimetres.
