OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FAnother was bludgeoned in the head
OL,7,Fafter being chased up the stairs as he
OL,8,Ftried to flee his attackers.
OL,10,FPaul Amoah, 39 of Hawthorn Close,
OL,11,FRedruth, was found guilty of attempted
OL,12,Fmurder, wounding with intent, and
OL,13,Faggravated burglary. He was sentenced
OL,14,Fto 27 years in prison.
OL,16,FLee Mitchell, 28 of Edmond Road,
OL,17,FRedruth, was found guilty of two
OL,18,Fcounts of wounding with intent and
OL,19,Faggravated burglary and was sentenced
OL,20,Fto nine years in prison.
