OL,3,CThree men who carried out 'frenzied'
OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FGavin Smale, 44 of Fore Street,
OL,7,FRedruth, was found guilty of unlawful
OL,8,Fwounding and aggravated burglary and
OL,9,Fwas sentenced to seven years in prison.
OL,11,FThe trio were convicted on 30 January
OL,12,Fat Truro Crown Court following a two-
OL,13,Fweek trial.
OL,15,FThe court heard how Amoah, Mitchell,
OL,16,Fand Smale broke into a property on
OL,17,FDrump Road in Redruth on 6 July 2023
OL,18,Farmed with a Baretta handgun and a
OL,19,Fhammer.
