OL,6,FJust eight minutes later, Amoah,
OL,7,FMitchell, and Smale were seen
OL,8,Fscattering away from the house leaving
OL,9,Ftwo men seriously injured after having
OL,10,Fbeen shot and bludgeoned.
OL,12,FThe victims, who were known to the
OL,13,Foffenders, all lived at the property
OL,14,Fand had been at home when Amoah and
OL,15,FMitchell knocked on the back door.
