OL,3,CThree men who carried out 'frenzied'
OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FOne of the occupants in the house said
OL,7,Fhe could see a figure at the back door
OL,8,Fholding a gun and raised the alarm to
OL,9,Fthe other occupants, just as Amoah and
OL,10,FMitchell started breaking down the
OL,11,Fback door.
OL,13,FOnce inside, Amoah and Mitchell, who
OL,14,Fwere wearing balaclavas, began their
OL,15,Fviolent attack, with Amoah shooting
OL,16,Fone of the victims in the back as he
OL,17,Ftried to flee.
OL,19,FMitchell chased down another victim as
OL,20,Fhe ran upstairs by hitting him
OL,21,Frepeatedly over the head with a hammer.
