OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FAfter hearing the attack, a third
OL,7,Fvictim barricaded himself in his room
OL,8,Fupstairs but sustained a cut to the
OL,9,Fhead after one of the offenders tried
OL,10,Fto force his way into his room.
OL,12,FThe men then ransacked the house
OL,13,Ftaking hundreds of pounds and one of
OL,14,Fthe victim's passports.
OL,16,FThe gunshot victim was rushed to
OL,17,Fhospital with life-threatening
OL,18,Finjuries, and underwent multiple
OL,19,Foperations and blood transfusions.
