OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FOne of the victims sustained
OL,7,Flacerations to his head and arms in
OL,8,Fthe hammer attack.
OL,10,FPolice were alerted by the ambulance
OL,11,Fservice with reports that a man had
OL,12,Fbeen shot in the back and armed
OL,13,Fresponse officers were deployed to the
OL,14,Fscene, and a manhunt was launched.
OL,16,FSmale was located and arrested a short
OL,17,Fwhile later in a field. Meanwhile,
OL,18,FAmoah was found after hiding under a
OL,19,Fsofa at an address on Cardew Close.
