OL,3,CThree men who carried out 'frenzied'
OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FMitchell was arrested the next day,
OL,7,Fand all the suspects were taken into
OL,8,Fcustody, charged and remanded.
OL,10,FFollowing searches inside the property
OL,11,Fon Harmony Close, a handgun was found
OL,12,Fwrapped in cloth in a children's toy
OL,13,Fbasket. DNA evidence on the gun proved
OL,14,Fto be Amoah's.
OL,16,FA hammer left behind at the crime
OL,17,Fscene was found to have Mitchell's DNA
OL,18,Fevidence on it along with the victim's
OL,19,Fblood.
