OL,3,CThree men who carried out 'frenzied'
OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Dave Egan, senior
OL,7,Finvestigating officer, said: "Amoah
OL,8,Fkept a dangerous firearm at his home
OL,9,Fwithout fear.
OL,11,F"He brazenly took it out on the
OL,12,Fstreets and into another person's home
OL,13,Fwith the intent on causing serious
OL,14,Fharm to someone who, when faced with
OL,15,Fsuch a weapon, had no choice but to
OL,16,Fflee resulting in him to be shot in
OL,17,Fthe back as he did so.
