OL,6,F"The victim suffered extremely
OL,7,Fserious, life-threatening injuries,
OL,8,Fhad to go through multiple operations
OL,9,Fand is extremely lucky to be alive
OL,10,Ftoday. He avoided being killed by a
OL,11,Fcouple of millimetres.
OL,13,F"While firearms offences are extremely
OL,14,Frare in this county, sadly we see all
OL,15,Ftoo often people losing their lives or
OL,16,Fbeing seriously injured through drug-
OL,17,Frelated violence.
