OL,3,CThree men who carried out 'frenzied'
OL,4,Cgun and hammer attack jailed
OL,6,F"It should also send a message that if
OL,7,Fyou arm yourself with any kind of a
OL,8,Fweapon, the chances are you will end
OL,9,Fup behind bars, seriously or fatally
OL,10,Fhurting someone, or getting seriously
OL,11,Fhurt yourself. It really isn't worth
OL,12,Fthe risk."
OL,14,FIf you have any information or
OL,15,Fconcerns about someone carrying a
OL,16,Fweapon, you can report it to Devon and
OL,17,FCornwall Police online , or 999 in an
OL,18,Femergency.
